                  <summary><p>The <title xml:lang="sa">Caturvargacintāmaṇi</title> is a 13<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> century <term xml:lang="sa">dharmanibandha</term> attributed to <persName xml:lang="sa">Hemādri</persName>. It was edited by <persName xml:lang="sa">Bharatacandra Śiromaṇi</persName> in 1871.</p>
<p>This is a 1985 reprint of volume 1, which contains the <title xml:lang="sa">Dānakhaṇḍa</title>. According to the <locus facs="6">library stamp</locus>, it was acquired by the Asiatic Society in 1986 and digitized by the Digital Library of India  in 2015.</p></summary>
                  
